    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Inflated, leather-covered, laceless balls used in the game of volleyball and generally 26 to 27 inches in circumference.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
